name: Kuchiki Rukia TI
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to generate Rukia Kuchiki from Bleach. Use Rukia to activate the embedding.

This was trained with a dataset that Included 40 pictures using the NAI model. It was mainly trained on her face and upper body.

I used a small dataset because I'm new to this and wanted to experiment. I liked the results of the training and wanted to post it here. I will continue to train other characters and I'm sure it will Improve over time.

Example Images generated using FusionDanceAnime By AURat:

https://civitai.com/models/3958/fusiondanceanime

Negative embedding used in the negatives: https://huggingface.co/datasets/Nerfgun3/bad_prompt
